
<tal:block condition="not: context/rcstype">

  <p class="portalMessage">
    No revision control details recorded for <span
    tal:replace="context/displayname">evolution MAIN</span>
  </p>

  <p>If upstream is maintained in CVS or SVN, then you will need to
  provide us with the location of the upstream branch so that it can be
  imported into the Bazaar. Please do so
  <a tal:attributes="href
  string:/products/${context/product/name}/+series/${context/name}/+source">
    here
  </a>. Once you have provided us with revision control details for this
  upstream branch, we can import that branch into
  <a href="/bazaar/">The Bazaar</a>, and HCT will be able to work with
  packages based on it.</p>

</tal:block>

<tal:block tal:condition="context/rcstype">

  <p>We have the following revision control system details on file for the
  branch:</p>

  <table class="listing">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th></th>
        <th>Details</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><b>Revision Control:</b></td>
        <td><b tal:content="context/rcstype/title">CVS</b>
            <b>(<span tal:replace="context/rcstype/name" />)</b></td>
      </tr>
        <tal:block condition="python:context.rcstype.name=='CVS'">
          <tr>
            <td>CVS Root:</td>
            <td tal:content="context/cvsroot">cvs root</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>CVS Module:</td>
            <td tal:content="context/cvsmodule">cvs module</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>CVS Branch:</td>
            <td tal:content="context/cvsbranch">cvs branch</td>
          </tr>
        </tal:block>
        <tal:block condition="python:context.rcstype.name=='SVN'">
          <tr>
            <td>Subversion Repository:</td>
            <td tal:content="context/svnrepository">svn repo</td>
          </tr>
        </tal:block>
        <tr>
          <td><b>Bazaar Publishing:</b></td>
          <td tal:content="context/importstatus/title">Publishing</td>
        </tr>
        <tal:block condition="context/branch">
          <tr>
            <td><b>Bazaar Branch:</b></td>
            <td tal:content="context/branch/getPackageName">foo bar</td>
          </tr>
        </tal:block>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</tal:block>
